+Below are the targeted changes to implement your requests. I have carefully traced the workflow from the frontend down to the `TiMini` protocol parameters.
+
+### 1. Database & API Changes (Printer Configuration)
+
+First, we need to extend the SQLite schema to save the printer settings and use them when dispatching the print job.
