+### 3. Settings UI, Aspect Ratio & Fit-to-Width (`PropertiesPanel.jsx`)
+
+When no item is selected, we show Canvas *and* Printer settings. When an image is selected, we lock the aspect ratio. When text is selected, we add the "Fit to Width" button that calculates the exact font size visually.
+
+**Update `PropertiesPanel.jsx`:** Replace the `if (!selectedItem)` block and update the Image/Text property renderers.
+
