+
+#### 5. Frontend: Add Control to Properties Panel
+*File: `frontend/src/components/PropertiesPanel.jsx`*
+Add a dropdown to change the global default font in the Canvas & Printer config tab.
+
+```javascript
+// --- frontend/src/components/PropertiesPanel.jsx ---
